Chancellors could soon be granted more powers under new regulations to govern universities. Education CS Fred Matiang&rsquo;i (pictured) said the ministry has been working on regulations to reform public university management.He said he wants VCs&rsquo; recruitment to be more inclusive. Matiang&rsquo;i spoke at the Chancellors Second Roundtable Discussion on Policies, Regulations and Standards for University Education. He said some people hold positions of VC, but lack confidence.